subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Amélie Mauresmo was upset by Victoria Azarenka, 6-2, 6-1, in the first round of the Zurich Open. Maria Kirilenko ousted Daniela Hantuchova, 7-5, 6-2, and Alona Bondarenko beat Alize Cornet, 1-6, 6-3, 7-6 (6), in the only other first-round matches indoors at Hallenstadion.
